      • Version

        public Version(java.lang.String format,
               java.lang.String file,
               java.lang.String query)
        Creates the Version with the format.

        If the format is 'file', then the file is queried with the query to retrieve the version-information.

        Parameters:
        format - one of the following are legal: exe, file
        file - empty if format is not file, else the relative path within the gamefolder of the Game has to be given
        query - - empty if format is not file, else the query within the file to determine the version has to be given
        Since:
        1.0
